# Upstream PRs trigger

When the user says **"Create PRs for upstream"** (or equivalent: open upstream PRs, PR fork branches to parent):

1. Read and follow `.cursor/skills/upstream-prs/SKILL.md` immediately.
2. Do not skip the confirmation step before creating PRs.
3. Use `gh` for all GitHub operations; one PR per solution branch.
